u-1 }. Then there exists an invertible module \mathscr { L } ' on X whose n-th tensor power is isomorphic to \mathscr { L } (if n is coprime to the residual characteristic of k=k( \mathscr { L } )).

Set V= \mathfrak {m}^ 
